      "instructions": "Always use code-search tools for ALL code discovery. Use code-search_code_search for natural language queries. Use code-search_code_graph_* for dependency analysis. NEVER use grep, ripgrep, rg, glob, find, ls, cat, bash, or any shell-based search.",
